A vintage-style illustration of a vast Pacific Ocean view from an airplane window at twilight, with the horizon split dramatically between deep indigo night sky on one side and warm golden sunset on the other, a faint dotted line suggesting an invisible boundary across the water below, wispy clouds catching both moonlight and sunrays simultaneously, the airplane wing visible at the edge of the frame casting shadows in two different directions, rendered in muted retro travel poster colors with subtle grain texture.
